{"tid":1300340,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【保護同路人】快啲入黎！！","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:34:58.000Z","uid":112405,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5714c996da55c17b9c096b51cd0db34bd54f03","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"雖然有啲長，但希望你地會睇落去。<br />\n<br />\n我經常發夢、遊行，睇見黑警啲行為都好嬲。但個人一直嬲都係對件事嘅發展冇乜幫助，當平心靜氣、理性咁諗下:<br />\n<br />\n圍警總、對峙時鬧警察，鬧嘅目的係咩？情緒宣洩、表達警察嘅不滿，定係想鬧到佢地良心覺醒？如果係後者，鬧住黎教、批評唔係個個人都接受到，特別係自尊心高、權力地位大過你嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇聽過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「標籤理論」</span></strong>？大概係話當人被貼上標籤後，會令人開始自我轉變，令自己嘅行為更符合標籤嘅描述。<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(如有講錯，請指正)</span><br />\n我覺得就好似我地不斷標籤警察做「黑警」咁，咁佢地就自我實現，慢慢變成「真黑警」，將戾氣發洩係示威者身上。咁當然，你可以係話咁係佢地個人質素問題，但我地係咪都有啲方法去避免呢啲情況或減少對自己嘅不利呢？<span style=\"color: orange;\">試諗下，村口隻惡狗吠你，你會唔會繼續挑釁隻狗，引佢去咬你？係，係隻狗唔啱，但蝕底嘅係邊個？</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武行為，必要時先做，平時就養精蓄銳。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n隔離post有講分化警察，我覺得可行。做得啱嘅讚，做得錯嘅彈；等做錯嘅人自己反省(如果佢有腦的話)；成效未必大，但起碼可以等其他警察有一絲嘅猶豫同思考空間，比個機會佢地反思自己。冇得救嘅人仍然係會冇得救的。<br />\n<br />\n上面嘅野可能會比人話我左膠和理非，但我目的只係唔想示威者再受傷、再受到不必要武力對待。減少挑動警察情緒，引致班友發癲，而最後受傷嘅係一班同路人。大家對呢個警權過大、監察制度失效、官官相衛嘅情況好憤怒、條氣好唔順，所以我覺得完全唔鬧警察係冇可能，我都會鬧，至於鬧嘅程度，就由自己判斷啦。至於更高尚嘅層面、咩道德感化果類野，我自問EQ低做唔黎，特別係對住啲同流合污嘅人。<br />\n至於對住真黑警，我唔會叫人以直報怨、跟規則投訴。因為而家個監警制度已經壽終正寢。<span style=\"color: red;\">以怨報怨、表揚黑警、禍必及妻兒。</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真黑警死全家</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n可能對警隊嘅憤怒係令一部分人上街嘅原因，我咁講好似滅緊火，但我地更應該將件事指向警隊背後嘅制度，呢個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">失效、互相縱容包庇嘅制度更值得我地憤怒</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對仲有良知、會思考嘅警察嘅說話:</strong><br />\n警隊係一個團體、政府紀律部隊，你地網頁上聲稱嘅目標、抱負、價值觀去晒邊？「人必自侮，然後人侮之」，睇返你地一直以黎嘅事蹟就明點解你地咁討人厭。一滴墨汁就可染黑一碗水，你地冇人可以獨善其身。當你地受到不禮貌對待時，唔好怪示威者；要怪就怪果班唔克制、唔專業嘅「同袍」連累你地、怪高層包庇、怪政府當你地做政治工具。覺得自己執勤十幾鐘、好辛苦又比人鬧，所以發洩係可諒解時，唔該諗返你地係受薪嘅，職務係包埋保持理性、克制、專業。你地覺得自己都係人、都有情緒、想被體諒前，唔該先企係示威者角度諗下：一班人冇錢收，甚至貼埋錢出黎示威、表達訴求、幫香港人(記住係幫埋你地)爭取自由公義時，反而比你地暴打。自己交稅出糧比人打自己？邊個唔嬲？仲要冇得還手，你地打人就冇後果，示威者掂下你地就襲警被捕，公平咩？鬧你地幾句算得係咩？你地應該先體諒示威者，而唔係要求示威者體諒你地。<br />\n<br />\n破窗效應：「環境中的不良現象如果被放任存在，就會誘使人們仿效，甚至變本加厲。」(引用自維基百科) 有人做錯事，你地唔及時制止，就會愈黎愈多人效法、情況唔受控。<span style=\"color: red;\">樹大有枯枝，警隊自己知</span>。見到同袍有唔啱嘅行為時，唔該你地阻止下，挽回少少聲譽。群眾嘅眼光係雪亮嘅。<br />\n<br />\n最後，想同自稱有抱負、有良知、想改變警隊嘅人講：你加左入一個從內到外都腐敗不堪嘅團體，一滴清水加入大染缸，你憑咩覺得自己可以出於污泥而不染時，又有能力改變呢一缸墨汁？點解唔試下加入司馬光團體，<span style=\"color: red;\">從外面打爛呢個缸</span>呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">頭盔：我唔鼓勵犯法</span><br />\n文筆唔好，可能表達得唔清晰，請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR：減少標籤「黑警」，減少同路人受傷機會。養精蓄銳。應讚則讚，以怨報怨，真黑警死全家。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就算政府冷處理，我地都唔應該全民休養生息，大家盡力去做其他事、各區連儂牆、支持各種活動、抵制出賣者、文宣、教育、大和解，遍地開花，但唔可以滿足於現狀，因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">訴求一個都未達成</span></span></strong>，黎緊仲有周圍裝天眼、社會信用評分制度等等嘅事要去抗爭。前路漫漫，我地香港人要並肩同行、不離不棄，齊心合力打呢場持久戰。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好愛香港，更愛香港人。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"890fe82589ac38bac40f6e89d4b2d74c48773050","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"［分析］歷史一直在重演 &amp; 鬼 &amp; 高官心態<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300313</a><br />\n<br />\n認真post冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠post就係咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036e1f1ea8859ff893a5e6a01cdcb1fc1d6b8450","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890fe82589ac38bac40f6e89d4b2d74c48773050","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"［分析］歷史一直在重演 &amp; 鬼 &amp; 高官心態<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300313</a><br />\n<br />\n認真post冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠post就係咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"我都係個認真嘅人，可能說話唔啱連登仔風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68f507ccf627d8db11522693600756f53071573","tid":1300340,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"得閒表揚下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40cbfaa95bbf89edf56fa7b8f6e1ae704e5e97e","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"幫手推得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4b74eabe9b2fb2d0adb51d49949470726f3bae","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036e1f1ea8859ff893a5e6a01cdcb1fc1d6b8450","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890fe82589ac38bac40f6e89d4b2d74c48773050","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"［分析］歷史一直在重演 &amp; 鬼 &amp; 高官心態<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300313</a><br />\n<br />\n認真post冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠post就係咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"我都係個認真嘅人，可能說話唔啱連登仔風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"尋日個個喺度屌曬鬼，今日又推埋啲on膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93af246bf27f36acd86075a8f14bf5fa5f686c29","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13da194bf33e2fbede460b8a1733b2ef0cdd5184","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4b74eabe9b2fb2d0adb51d49949470726f3bae","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036e1f1ea8859ff893a5e6a01cdcb1fc1d6b8450","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890fe82589ac38bac40f6e89d4b2d74c48773050","tid":1300340,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"［分析］歷史一直在重演 &amp; 鬼 &amp; 高官心態<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300313</a><br />\n<br />\n認真post冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膠post就係咁推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"我都係個認真嘅人，可能說話唔啱連登仔風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"尋日個個喺度屌曬鬼，今日又推埋啲on膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"尋日真係多膠post，今日好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba997b59f523979cd5e3c7b2c985b8bbf27cb77","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4759c01c77c07d15f272c965e29ddabea3e4e618","tid":1300340,"uid":120537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"「對仲有良知、會思考嘅警察嘅說話」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知你係好天真好傻定高級洗白<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦標咩籤理論啫丟個term出嚟就勁啲有說服力啲？<br />\n市民唔叫黑警咁警隊入面就會停止標籤打鳩示威者=好警察？你覺得市民對黑驚影響力大啲定黑警圍內？"},{"pid":"56e20e7bcb8e42f487429a45156379f64082a216","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4759c01c77c07d15f272c965e29ddabea3e4e618","tid":1300340,"uid":120537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"「對仲有良知、會思考嘅警察嘅說話」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知你係好天真好傻定高級洗白<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦標咩籤理論啫丟個term出嚟就勁啲有說服力啲？<br />\n市民唔叫黑警咁警隊入面就會停止標籤打鳩示威者=好警察？你覺得市民對黑驚影響力大啲定黑警圍內？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"下，有幾天真？唔知你有冇睇晒成段啦。我信警隊入面仲有有思想嘅人，不過佢地都係抵鬧咁解。佢地入得警隊就預左比人指罵，食得咸魚抵得渴。世界唔係非黑即白架，等於唔係所有法官都係正義有良知咁。<br />\n<br />\n冇話勁啲有說服力啲，效果可能唔大，但我係提出一個諗法覺得worth a try。所以我前面有講，其實都係想打心理戰、分化警察。影響力果到，點解唔兩方面都做？<br />\n我都好唔忿氣，所以我對啲大快人心，好治癒既事絕對唔反感架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54202fda7130726e2f2f9a1496d11df3747acd41","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02af67fe429f103b46549a3f860a91d09eb2323a","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f3176cae42c677716471bfaad4f5524d7055f3","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d82fd03eb7d33a71869cb75bccacc6d9df6905","tid":1300340,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}